<div id="review_1448627478" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1448627478" />
    <a title="Les Donovan" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/49094581-les-donovan"><img alt="Les Donovan" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_50x66-632230dc9882b4352d753eedf9396530.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1448627478?book_show_action=true">Nov 21, 2015</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Les Donovan" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Les Donovan" href="/user/show/49094581-les-donovan">Les Donovan</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1448627478" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14303649147205227389">A must read! A fast pacing intriguing story that you will not be able to put down. Mark Donovan has done a fantastic job of coupling high technology with bio-tourism to tell a story that’s not only riveting but could be true in today’s world of geopolitics. The suspense starts on page one and continues to the very end. It is a must read for those that enjoy a real thriller. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


